    correction: "(a) $a = -0{,}2$, $b = 0{,}4$. Solution d'équilibre : $C_p = -\\dfrac{0{,}4}{-0{,}2} = 2$.\n\nSolution générale : $C(t) = K\\,\\mathrm{e}^{-0{,}2t} + 2$.\n\nCondition initiale : $C(0) = K + 2 = 1 \\Rightarrow K = -1$.\n\nSolution : $C(t) = -\\mathrm{e}^{-0{,}2t} + 2 = 2 - \\mathrm{e}^{-0{,}2t}$.\n\n(b) La concentration d'équilibre est $\\displaystyle\\lim_{t \\to +\\infty} C(t) = 2\\,\\mathrm{mg/L}$.\n\n(c) $2 - \\mathrm{e}^{-0{,}2t} = 1{,}8 \\Rightarrow \\mathrm{e}^{-0{,}2t} = 0{,}2 \\Rightarrow -0{,}2t = \\ln(0{,}2) = -\\ln 5$.\n\n$t = \\dfrac{\\ln 5}{0{,}2} = 5\\ln 5 \\approx 8{,}05$ heures."
