      correction: "$$\\int_0^{\\pi/2} \\sin^2(x)\\,\\mathrm{d}x = \\int_0^{\\pi/2} \\frac{1-\\cos(2x)}{2}\\,\\mathrm{d}x$$\n$$= \\frac{1}{2}\\Big[x - \\frac{\\sin(2x)}{2}\\Big]_0^{\\pi/2} = \\frac{1}{2}\\left(\\frac{\\pi}{2} - \\frac{\\sin(\\pi)}{2} - 0\\right) = \\frac{\\pi}{4}$$"
