    correction: "$X$ suit une loi binomiale $\\mathcal{B}\\!\\left(5,\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$.\n$P(X=3) = \\binom{5}{3} \\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right)^3 \\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right)^2 = 10 \\times \\frac{1}{32} = \\frac{10}{32} = \\frac{5}{16} \\approx 0{,}3125$."
