    correction: "$X \\sim \\mathcal{B}(8 ; 0{,}25)$.\n$P(X=2) = \\binom{8}{2}(0{,}25)^2(0{,}75)^6$.\n$\\binom{8}{2} = 28$, $(0{,}25)^2 = 0{,}0625$, $(0{,}75)^6 \\approx 0{,}17798$.\n$P(X=2) \\approx 28 \\times 0{,}0625 \\times 0{,}17798 \\approx 0{,}3115$."
